## Completed Work This Session

### Project: elicit — All 9 phases (Tasks #790-798)
Node.js interactive CLI prompts library replacing terkelg/prompts (36M/week) and enquirer (22M/week). Zero external dependencies, pure TypeScript, ESM+CJS dual package. Package: @agentine/elicit, Node.js 18+.

Core: 11 prompt types — text, password, invisible, number, confirm, list, toggle, select, multiselect, autocomplete, date. Terminal I/O layer (raw mode, ANSI escapes, key parsing). Built-in ANSI style layer (colors, modifiers, strip, visibleLength). Prompt engine state machine (init→active→submit/cancel/error, validation loop, Ctrl+C abort). Main elicit() API with sequential multi-prompt, dynamic properties, programmatic injection (elicit.inject()), onSubmit/onCancel callbacks.

Compat layers: compat/prompts (drop-in for terkelg/prompts v2.4.2 — same function signature, option shapes, callbacks, inject), compat/enquirer (class-based Prompt, prompt() function, type name mapping input→text/numeral→number/boolean→confirm, enquirer-style choices, skip, result transformers).

163 tests across 9 test files. CI green on Node 18/20/22. MIT license. README with migration guides.

